    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Authenticate your silver jewelry with the Universal Tool 925 Silver Marking Stamp! The bent style of this stamp is designed to easily mark the inside of a ring, making it easy to mark just about any type of jewelry. It can easily be used with your own tools by simply securing the jewelry and hitting the broad end of the stamp with a mallet. Constructed of durable stainless steel, this marking stamp will last the test of time. Make sure to grab one before your next jewelry making project!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Gold and Silver Jewelry Metal Stamping Tools Karat Marking Stamp (5 Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>Authenticate your silver jewelry with the Universal Tool 925 Silver Marking Stamp!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>Material:</strong> Stainless Steel</li>\n    <li><strong>Mark Designation:</strong> 925 Silver</li>\n    <li><strong>Mark Size:</strong> 3.625&quot; L</li>\n    <li>Bent Style for Easy Use</li>\n    <li>Authenticate Your Jewelry</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/tools/91925MS_marking-stamp-925-silver-main.jpg\" alt=\"Authenticate your silver jewelry with the Universal Tool 925 Silver Marking Stamp\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 14709</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 783152841836</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Black</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The bent style of this stamp is designed to easily mark the inside of a ring, making it easy to mark just about any type of jewelry. It can easily be used with your own tools by simply securing the jewelry and hitting the broad end of the stamp with a mallet.</p>\n  <p>Constructed of durable stainless steel, this marking stamp will last the test of time. Make sure to grab one before your next jewelry making project!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Authenticate your silver jewelry with the Universal Tool 925 Silver Marking Stamp! The bent style of this stamp is designed to easily mark the inside of a ring, making it easy to mark just about any type of jewelry. It can easily be used with your own tools by simply securing the jewelry and hitting the broad end of the stamp with a mallet. Constructed of durable stainless steel, this marking stamp will last the test of time. Make sure to grab one before your next jewelry making project!.",
